body_html:
Thanks for the links. "TensorFlow vs Our" differences, with "Our" meaning tflite, could be important documentation for anyone trying to use tflite. I guess we can close this, since the differences are obviously known.
kOHWI, // Our standard for conv weights
kHWIO, // TensorFlow conv weights
k1HWO, // Our standard for DepthwiseConv weights
kHWIM, // TensorFlow DepthwiseConv weights
